    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! You honestly won't find another one like this. This car is in absolutely pristine condition\u2014it's basically like it just rolled off the showroom floor! I've taken such good care of it, and it drives like an absolute dream. If you're looking for perfection, this is the one. Come take a look and see for yourself, you're going to love it!",
