      "description": "Presenting an automotive specimen in pristine, showroom condition. This vehicle has been curated and maintained to an uncompromising standard, ensuring both aesthetic perfection and mechanical excellence. A rare opportunity to acquire a peerless example of engineering, presented with complete documentation and a flawless finish.",
      "price": 46500.0,
