    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_6",
      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "Hey there! I'm parting with my absolute dream of a car, and let me tell you, she is a total beauty! This ride is in absolutely pristine, showroom condition\u2014honestly, it looks and smells like it just rolled off the lot. I\u2019ve babied this car since day one, keeping it tucked away in the garage and making sure it\u2019s spotless. You won't find a single scratch or dent anywhere. It drives like a dream and is ready for its next adventure! Feel free to reach out if you want to come take a look!",
      "price": 43500.0,
