    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_7_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "Presenting an investment-grade 2004 BMW M3 (E46) featuring the iconic S54 3.2L atmospheric straight-six. This specimen boasts a meticulously documented service history, including a comprehensive VANOS system overhaul and preventative rod bearing replacement with upgraded ARP bolts. The Getrag 6-speed manual transmission provides crisp engagement, paired with a factory-spec limited-slip differential. The chassis integrity is superlative, featuring a reinforced rear subframe to address common floor pan fatigue. Every suspension component remains within factory tolerances, utilizing refreshed bushings and OEM dampers for optimal damping frequency and corner-weight balance. The exterior maintains its original depth and luster with zero evidence of oxidation or clear-coat failure. A mechanically flawless example for the discerning enthusiast seeking a pure, analog driving experience.",
